title: Australia pivots on climate with 2050 net zero target, but won't adopt steeper 2030 commitment
content:
1. Australia pivots on climate with 2050 net zero target, but won't adopt steeper 2030 commitment  The Washington Post
  2. Australia Pledges ‘Net Zero’ Emissions by 2050. Its Plan Makes That Hard to Believe.  The New York Times

  4. Australia adopts target of net zero carbon emissions by 2050 but won't make it law  NBC News
  5. We’ve spent a year waiting for this 2050 climate plan and it’s actually just the status quo with some new speculative graphs  The Guardian Australia
